{
  "stem": "2002.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was bleeding, but I survived.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It wasn't that bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But to make a story that many times the Jewish people would have to-- we used to have instead curtains or anything, we used to have, outside, we used to have wood covered the glass.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like swinging-- I don't know how to explain that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Shutters.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Shutters.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's fine.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And many times they were closed, because they would throw in rocks in the windows.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I gave you an example.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The people who lived-- who was my friend, who-- who told me to go work with him in the field, this was a [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he liked me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said, Hitler's comin', but, Jack, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you I'll save.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The other Jews, I'll help Hitler.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was his-- to show his love to me, to tell me that he's gonna help kill all other Jews, but he's gonna save me.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was in 1939, just before-- just before the war.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1939 was a tremendous anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We only knew-- about-- we didn't-- that's a good question.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't know too much before.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like, I didn't know-- maybe a year, six months before.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But never did I ever dream that something like that would happen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, we knew it was problems, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But Holocaust, to-- to wipe, to take off a race from the-- from the world, just like that to destroy because you were Jewish, I never dreamt of.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] It started out that one of my brothers was a big Communist leader in the town.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was arrested many times just before May the 1st, because that's was the celebration.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "May the 1st the Communists would celebrate.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
